data.description: Looking for land outside of the city limits with utilities in place? Ditch the dirt roads and come see this 15.12 acres located off of a PAVED main road near the intersection of Hwy 171 and FM 67! Close proximity to city limits and NO ZONING! Could be used for commercial but currently has AG exemptions in place with low taxes! City water, conventional septic, and electric already in place with no known deed restrictions. Mobile home will convey with property but is not in livable condition. Come see it!
